OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early morning mist, fog and
OL,6,Flow cloud in the east will clear
OL,7,Fquickly after sunrise. Another bright
OL,8,Fand sunny day expected with
OL,9,Ftemperatures slightly higher than
OL,10,FThursday. Winds easing through the
OL,11,Fday, but staying gusty in the far
OL,12,Fsouthwest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA clear night to come with
OL,15,Fhigh cloud in the west. Patchy mist
OL,16,Fand fog developing in prone spots to
OL,17,Fthe east. A grass frost developing in
OL,18,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
